Detailed Description

Rendition attribute describing the current fill state (on or off.).

Warning:
Client code should not set the WT_Fill attribute. This is managed internally by specific drawables, as follows:
  • WT_Filled_Ellipse: If the fill mode is not set, it will be turned on.
  • WT_Outline_Ellipse: If the fill mode is set, it will be turned off.
  • WT_Polyline: If the fill mode is set, it will be turned off.
  • WT_Polygon: If the fill mode is not set, it will be turned on.
See also:
WT_Rendition
